high_descs: Turn around and walk to the chair closest to the door on the right side.
Pick up the set of keys closest to the edge of the chair.
Walk to the coffee table in the middle of the room.
Place the keys on coffee table to the left of the tissue box on the edge of the coffee table.
Turn and walk to the chair to the right of the door and face the side of the chair.
Pick up the keys that are in front of the remote.
Walk back to the coffee table in the middle of the room.
Place the keys on the coffee table and to the left of the first set of keys.
anns.task_desc: Move two sets of keys from the chair to the coffee table.

high_descs: Turn right, walk past the coffee table to the green chair with two key chains on it.
Pick up the key chain in the front from the chair.
Turn around and walk to the tissue boxes on the coffee table.
Put the key chain on the coffee table, to the left of the tissue box which is in front of the newspaper.
Turn around and walk back to the chair that you got the key chain from.
Pick up the other key chain from the chair.
Turn right and walk back to the coffee table.
Put the other key chain on the coffee table, to the left of the first key chain.
anns.task_desc: Move two key chains from a chair to a coffee table.
